Setting Type Description <code>OKTA_DOMAIN</code> <code>str</code> Your Okta domain (e.g., <code>dev-123456.okta.com</code>) <code>OIDC_RP_CLIENT_ID</code> <code>str</code> OAuth 2.0 client ID from Okta application <code>OIDC_RP_CLIENT_SECRET</code> <code>str</code> OAuth 2.0 client secret from Okta application <p>Example:</p> <pre><code>TINKUN_OIDC = {
    "OKTA_DOMAIN": "dev-123456.okta.com",
    "OIDC_RP_CLIENT_ID": "0oa1234567890abcdef",
    "OIDC_RP_CLIENT_SECRET": "very-secret-string-from-okta",
}
</code></pre>

Setting Type Default Description <code>OIDC_STATE_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNS"</code> State parameter cookie <code>OIDC_NONCE_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNN"</code> Nonce cookie <code>OIDC_ACCESS_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNA"</code> Access token cookie <code>OIDC_ID_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNI"</code> ID token cookie <code>OIDC_REFRESH_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNR"</code> Refresh token cookie <code>OIDC_CODE_VERIFIER_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNV"</code> PKCE code verifier cookie <code>OIDC_TEMP_ACCESS_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNTA"</code> Temporary access token (during refresh) <code>OIDC_TEMP_ID_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNTI"</code> Temporary ID token (during refresh) <code>OIDC_TEMP_REFRESH_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME</code> <code>str</code> <code>"TKNTR"</code> Temporary refresh token (during refresh) <p>Custom Cookie Names:</p> <pre><code>TINKUN_OIDC = {
    "OIDC_ACCESS_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME": "myapp_access",
    "OIDC_ID_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME": "myapp_id",
    "OIDC_REFRESH_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME": "myapp_refresh",
}
</code></pre>
